{"tid":1933554,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我整咗D英文文宣，希望可以減低海外亞洲人（包括香港人）被歧視嘅機會","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T04:44:37.000Z","uid":246588,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b93fa07cf84fdad9cf612adf9518a57b2eba14e","tid":1933554,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"呢度有3個系列:<br />\n<br />\n第一，鬼佬藍系列<br />\n<br />\n部分外國人可能超愛中國，程度同藍屍無異，希望可以將佢地拉番佢地做反共嘅人<br />\n好似杜生果條咁，唔少意大利人都好藍嘅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q5Dfz2GzHOY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ5Dfz2GzHOY&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=3b149b23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q5Dfz2GzHOY</a><br />\n<br />\n所以我整咗呢個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTDqNBt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTDqNBt.jpg&h=5d386b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有手足將佢翻譯做意大利文<br />\n<br />\n第二，與中國割蓆系列<br />\n<br />\n介紹亞洲人分好多種，例如日本人、韓國人、台灣人、香港人，與大陸人割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpoaYJ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpoaYJ2.jpg&h=d6a4fdb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比埋呢張吉嘅任你發揮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ye9NgvZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYe9NgvZ.jpg&h=b6e59d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，左膠或大中華膠系列<br />\n<br />\n講一D中共逼害中國人嘅歷史，令外國人無咁憎中國人，改為針對中共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOVqp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOVqp5.jpg&h=e18892e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望無問題、無打錯，請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"cb0b3b2ea1b06c2b931895e89bea60cd2d08b435","tid":1933554,"uid":211265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c3ab1e5878e765bdbd1cc587d4910d4f073ed06","tid":1933554,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,